To get an item encounter (regardless of spread), you might hit these frames for the item you're looking for 
(assuming having items are frame/PID specific and not species specific):

1) No special lead:
-Frame 919, slot 1 -> Aron (Hard Stone), Shuppet (Spell Tag), Magnemite (Metal Coat), Hariyama (King's Rock), Whismur (Chesto Berry), Trapinch (Soft Sand)
-Frame 1383, slot 0 -> Sandshrew (Quick Claw), Pooch (Pecha Berry)

2) Compound Eyes lead:
-Frame 856, slot 3 -> Abra (Twisted Spoon)
-Frame 4883, slot 11 -> Cacnea (Poison Barb), Skitty (Leppa Berry)


The locations where this would work would be:

-Route 116: Abra, Poochyena, Whismur, Skitty
-Granite Cave (B1F & B2F): Aron
-Route 111 (Desert): Sandshrew, Cacnea, Trapinch
-Victory Road (1F & B1F): Hariyama
-New Mauville (any): Magnemite
-Route 121: Shuppet


